For the 2018-2020 period, the current president of PEN Bangladesh is [[Syed Manzoorul Islam]], Rabindra University Vice Chancellor Biswajit Ghose, writer Ahmed Reza and Maleka Ferdousi were elected vice presidents while Ferdousi Mahmud and Lovely Bashar were elected joint secretaries general of the committee.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/city/syed-manzoorul-new-president-pen-bangladesh-1507231|title=Syed Manzoorul new president of Pen Bangladesh|date=2017-12-19|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2018-01-21|language=en}}</ref>
